channel.title: Euxoloti on it's way! Will anyone be building and selling?
channel.description:
I've been anticipating this project for ages and now after some recent investigating I see that the Euxoloti is on it's way!
It seems to be a pcb/panel set coming soon according to [irie electronics](http://irieelectronics.de/shop-offline/)
I'm curious if any one will be building and selling modules? DIY is okay with me but not when I've gotta source a ton of new parts and when it's all SMD - just not ready for that.
I'd love to hear from any buliders who may be building and selling modules in the upcoming months.
Cheers!
